  "A cliff diver jumps from a 45-meter cliff with an initial upward velocity of 8 m/s. h(t) = -5t^2 + 8t + 45. When does the diver hit the water?": "",
  "After about 3 seconds": "",
  "After about 5 seconds": "",
  "After about 4 seconds": "",
  "After about 3.9 seconds": "",
  "Set h = 0: -5t^2 + 8t + 45 = 0, or 5t^2 - 8t - 45 = 0. Using the quadratic formula: t = (8 + sqrt(64 + 900))/10 = (8 + sqrt(964))/10. Since sqrt(964) is about 31.05, t is about 39.05/10 = 3.9, which rounds to about 4 seconds.": "",
  "A farmer has 160 meters of fencing to create two adjacent rectangular pens (sharing one side). What total width maximizes the combined area?": "",
